Package: ebirdabund
Title: Estimate Relative Abundance from eBird Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("First", "Last", email = "example@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Estimates relative abundance of bird species within an arbitrary
    spatial polygon using eBird raw data, habitat covariates from ESA land cover
    and SRTM elevation, and generalized additive models (GAMs) with a negative
    binomial error distribution.
